            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="44661894">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <div class="ll">
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/44661894/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p44661894-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class="">1.中黄左右藏，当标作中黄、左右藏。 2.鄴中黄左右藏，当标作鄴、中黄、左右藏。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-06-07 11:54</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p>1.中黄左右藏，当标作中黄、左右藏。</p><p>2.鄴中黄左右藏，当标作鄴、中黄、左右藏。</p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p44661894-1.jpg"></div></div>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







